description:
SPECIAL 2 ON 1 MATCH UP
The Dragon takes on two for this special Tag Team match up. Isis Love and Gwen Diamond, teamed up, get 3 tag ins per round with 9 chances to double team the renowned Dragon and take her down.
This special match up has everything: submission holds, hardcore finger fucking during wrestling, and a down-to-the-last-second win. Does the Dragon get to fuck her two opponents or do they get to double fuck her? You'll have to join to find out..
title: The Dragon vs Isis Love "The Goddess" & Gwen Diamond "The Tornado"
